# WORK
IMAPStore work-remote
Host outlook.office365.com
Port 993
User craig.fielder@juvare.com
PassCmd "security find-generic-password -s ad -w"
SSLType IMAP
AuthMechs *
Timeout 120
PipelineDepth 50

MaildirStore work-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/mail/work/
Inbox ~/.local/mail/work/INBOX

Channel work
Master :work-remote:
Slave :work-local:
Patterns *
Create Slave
Expunge Slave
Sync All
